title: Politics / Baking: the future format of this channel?
description: Cambodian democracy, the conquest of Mosul, North Korea, Syria… should this channel transition to being a bit more of a foreign-policy news-desk?  Maybe.  This video discusses the future content and future format of this channel (that definitely WILL change, when I'm no longer broadcasting from within China).
